## 부팅시 실행되어 usb에 정보를 저장하는 script 작성 (#rc파일 #usb #su권한)


> 요청 사항 Mail
@code

안녕하세요. 김원균PM 입니다.

@강성민매니저님,
VOC 안정성에서 발생한 전체채널 시청불가 이슈 – EGLInitialize Error 에 대해,
Broadcom에서 메모리(v3d) 사용량이 비정상적으로 많다며 검토 요청이 왔습니다.

두 번째 첨부파일에 v3d 관련 내용 확인 요청 드려요

감사합니다.
김원균드림

Update By: Jason Lim(Broadcom Corporation)
Update Time: 04-October-2024 03:22:00

Latest Response: 
Hi Kim WonKyun,
 
You can check memory information by the following ways. (rmlmk log / log message of NEXUS / BHPA memory / memory utilization on each appliction)
I guess you can find which application's memory is growing.
 
-. enable rmlmk relevant log messages in nxserver.cpp (vendor/broadcom/bcm_platform/nxif/nxserver)
    #define USAGE_PER_CLIENT 1
    #define USAGE_FULL_DETAILS 1
-. enanbling log messages
$ su
# echo "nexus_memory msg" > /proc/brcm/debug
# echo "nexus_memory_cache msg" > /proc/brcm/debug
-. monitoring BHPA memory. please call "cat /sys/kernel/debug/bhpa" every 1min
$ su
# cat /sys/kernel/debug/bhpa
-. monitoring memory utilization on each appliction
# dumpsys meminfo
 
Thanks,
Jason Lim


Hi Kim WonKyun,
 
Please check "cat /sys/kernel/debug/dri/0/*/client" too. This "DRI" is related to V3D memory on applications.
 
-. monitoring BHPA memory. please call "cat /sys/kernel/debug/bhpa" &  "cat /sys/kernel/debug/dri/0/*/client" every 1min
$ su
# cat /sys/kernel/debug/bhpa
# cat /sys/kernel/debug/dri/0/*/client

@endcode

> USB에 저장하는 스크립트 추가

@code
1. rc파일에 등록 시작 
- X:\SKB\kaon_bcm_androidtv12\device\broadcom\K1100UA\rcs\init.rmag.rc

on property:dev.eth0.init=1 && property:dev.cm.ni.init=2
    setprop vendor.nx.fe.state 1
    start networkmonitor
	start checkmemory
	
service checkmemory /system/bin/checkmemory
   class main
   user root
   group root
   disabled
   seclabel u:r:su:s0	#su권한 추가

2. 빌드 추가 
- X:\SKB\kaon_bcm_androidtv12\vendor\kaon\kaon.mk
# scripts in prebuilts
PRODUCT_PACKAGES += cmconnectioncheck
PRODUCT_PACKAGES += networkmonitor
PRODUCT_PACKAGES += checkmemory

- X:\SKB\kaon_bcm_androidtv12\vendor\kaon\prebuilts\scripts\Android.mk
# checkmemory
include $(CLEAR_VARS)
LOCAL_MODULE := checkmemory
LOCAL_MODULE_CLASS := EXECUTABLES
LOCAL_MODULE_TAG := optional
LOCAL_SRC_FILES := checkmemory
LOCAL_STRIP_MODULE := false
LOCAL_PRELINK_MODULE := false
include $(BUILD_PREBUILT)

3. 스크립트 작성
- X:\SKB\kaon_bcm_androidtv12\vendor\kaon\prebuilts\scripts\checkmemory
#!/system/bin/sh

loga "checkmemory."
echo "nexus_memory_cache msg" > /proc/brcm/debug
loga "checkmemory.."
echo "nexus_memory msg" > /proc/brcm/debug
loga "checkmemory..."
function loga() {
    /system/bin/logwrapper echo "${@}"
}

while true; do
    loga "checkmemory...."
    MOUNT_PATH=$(mount | grep '/storage/' | grep -v 'emulated' | awk '{print $3}')
    if [ ! -z "$MOUNT_PATH" ]; then
        LOG_FILE="$MOUNT_PATH/memory_info.log"

            echo "========================================" >> $LOG_FILE
            date >> $LOG_FILE

        echo "======== /sys/kernel/debug/bhpa ========" >> $LOG_FILE
        cat /sys/kernel/debug/bhpa >> $LOG_FILE

        echo "=== /sys/kernel/debug/dri/0/*/client ===" >> $LOG_FILE
        cat /sys/kernel/debug/dri/0/*/client >> $LOG_FILE

        loga "Log write : $LOG_FILE"
    else
        loga "No USB."
    fi

    sleep 60
done
@endcode

